ar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#8-2","id":"1263221","time":"2017-7-14 00:22","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"把信息encode到大肠杆菌里发射到外太空"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/52/315266.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1263050","time":"2017-7-13 14:59","userId":"art_forest","userName":"无心的观测者","userSign":"(我想成为创作者，比起仅仅当一个观众 ... ...)","message":"我看完了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">，E.coli的分裂太频繁了，90%的还原度很正常，不过没有写养了多久差评。<br>把E.coli这种臭臭的东西当做硬盘，不觉得有点恶心吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">如果把对象换成人，就是很好的科幻小说素材</span><br>还有<div class=\"quote\"><q>1Disclosure: One of these researchers is married to a WIRED editor.</q></div>这是什么鬼<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/75/77515.jpg","floor":"#9-1","id":"1263061","time":"2017-7-13 15:37","userId":"th3ta","userName":"th3ta \"Paradox\"","userSign":"","message":"<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">可能被那个editor退过稿？</span><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/52/315266.jpg","floor":"#9-2","id":"1263067","time":"2017-7-13 15:52","userId":"art_forest","userName":"无心的观测者","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">th3ta \"Paradox\"</span> 说: 可能被那个editor退过稿？</q></div>这种连参考文献都不写的杂志，连SCI都不是，有付出这么大代价的价值吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#9-3","id":"1263081","time":"2017-7-13 17:12","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"养100代的话估计还原度还能剩多少？<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>那养1年不冻起来呢<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">?"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/52/315266.jpg","floor":"#9-4","id":"1263086","time":"2017-7-13 17:18","userId":"art_forest","userName":"无心的观测者","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 养100代的话估计还原度还能剩多少？<br>那养1年不冻起来呢?</q></div>大肠杆菌15min分裂一次，100代也才25hours，这还不够产生大量突变。<br>连续分裂一年，等于无限→0。不过这么连续养一年的结果是，菌种活力衰退(不长了)&大量突变<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#9-5","id":"1263089","time":"2017-7-13 17:22","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烦恼的观测者</span> 说: 大肠杆菌15min分裂一次，100代也才25hours，这还不够产生大量突变。<br>连续分裂一年，等于无限→0。不过这么连续养一年的结果是，菌种活力衰退(不长了)&amp;大量突变</q></div>因为不是学生物的不是很懂<br>那肠道菌群是怎么维持活力的？靠持续的选择吗？<br>在培养瓶里养的时候如果想连续养一年没什么办法吗？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/52/315266.jpg","floor":"#9-6","id":"1263099","time":"2017-7-13 17:57","userId":"art_forest","userName":"无心的观测者","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 因为不是学生物的不是很懂<br>那肠道菌群是怎么维持活力的？靠持续的选择吗？<br>在培养瓶里养的时候如果想连续养一年没什么办法吗？</q></div>因为肠道菌群不是一直在分裂（由于饥饿），有时间修复错误，而且可以与不同的菌之间嘿嘿嘿，保证遗传多样性。而培养基里一直摇的大肠杆菌会高速分裂，产生的错误得不到及时修复，而且单克隆的大肠杆菌多样性低，因此抗逆性差。<br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">阿勒，为啥我在bgm上讲这些<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"></span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/42/304246.jpg","floor":"#9-7","id":"1263100","time":"2017-7-13 18:01","userId":"304246","userName":"Rくん","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烦恼的观测者</span> 说: 因为肠道菌群不是一直在分裂（由于饥饿），有时间修复错误，而且可以与不同的菌之间嘿嘿嘿，保证遗传多样性。而培养基里一直摇的大肠杆菌会高速分裂，产生的错误得不到及时修复，而且单克隆的大肠杆菌多样性低，因此...</q></div>修复原来还和分裂速度这么大关系啊...<br>所以单克隆的话可以饥饿着养吧<br>然而快速分裂完赶紧冷藏起来似乎基本是更有用的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">茶话会不就是这样吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"></span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/52/315266.jpg","floor":"#9-8","id":"1263102","time":"2017-7-13 18:09","userId":"art_forest","userName":"无心的观测者","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Rくん</span> 说: 修复原来还和分裂速度这么大关系啊...<br>所以单克隆的话可以饥饿着养吧<br>然而快速分裂完赶紧冷藏起来似乎基本是更有用的<br>茶话会不就是这样吗</q></div>可以饥饿，低温会延长菌的生命周期。事实上我们就是把暂时不用的菌给冻在-80℃的，那些给各种细菌保种的中心也是先冻，冻几年之后拿出来再养，恢复一下活力，然后再冻起来<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/87/278770.jpg","floor":"#9-9","id":"1263199","time":"2017-7-13 23:14","userId":"278770","userName":"screnary-喵Bus","userSign":"","message":"回忆爱玛侬"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#9-10","id":"1263212","time":"2017-7-14 00:17","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"原论文应该有写？<br>逛着逛着又撞到一只phd..."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/52/315266.jpg","floor":"#9-11","id":"1263279","time":"2017-7-14 10:15","userId":"art_forest","userName":"无心的观测者","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">dhzy</span> 说: 原论文应该有写？<br>逛着逛着又撞到一只phd...</q></div>bgm居然还有phD，握手<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#9-12","id":"1263296","time":"2017-7-14 11:55","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烦恼的观测者</span> 说: bgm居然还有phD，握手</q></div>不我不是，我是说你是其中之一..."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/52/315266.jpg","floor":"#9-13","id":"1263321","time":"2017-7-14 15:46","userId":"art_forest","userName":"无心的观测者","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">dhzy</span> 说: 不我不是，我是说你是其中之一...</q></div>只要有phd我就很欣慰了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/